ygData.messageBody:
Check out Menkes Tobalet - he's an NPC that hangs out near the docks in S
Qeynos. Hail him and he will tell you what to bring him for different items
he makes. His Snake Fang Necklace will ward off poison - helpful when
hunting big bugs, etc.

Snyak
